  <Strings>
    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42156</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_030_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>オレらが行ったヴァルハラと、
この世界のヴァルハラ、ずいぶん違ったよな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>The Valhalla we first visited is so different from this time's Valhalla...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42264</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_030_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>わたしたちの時代のヴァルハラは
もっときれいだったけど</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Our era's Valhalla is definitely prettier but...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42364</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_030_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でも、この時代のヴァルハラの方が
温かかったよ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But this Valhalla is livelier and warmer, don't you think?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42468</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_030_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そうかな、オレはちょっと寒くて
上着欲しかったぜ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Is that what you think? The people seemed sad and they wear shabby clothes.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42580</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_030_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そういうことじゃなくて、
なんか人の心が温かかったってこと</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That's not what I'm talking about. The people's hearts are warm.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42676</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_030_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>私は貧しくても、
心が温かな方が好きだな……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I don't think they are in the best conditions but I prefer the warmth in their hearts!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42752</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_030_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>確かにそうかもだけど……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Sure, that may be the case, but...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42848</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_030_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でも、それってオレらが
よそ者だかんだろ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Aren't you looking it from a stranger's perspective?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42944</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_030_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>当人たちにしたら、
金のあった方がいいと思う</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>For the people involved, money actually matters.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43040</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_030_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>うーん……そう、なのかな……
そうかも……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Mmm...Is that...so?...You're right.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43128</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_030_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……でも、本当に
それでいいのかな？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But is this really how things should be?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
</SceneText>
